description	"Cassian Andor

^2Weaponry:
- SE-14c Blaster Pistol (2)
- A-280 Blaster Rifle (3)
- 2 Frag Grenades

^8Attributes:
- Melee Damage Reduction
- Cannot be seen via Sense
- Healing (2)

^3Abilities:
- Dodge (3)
- Disguise

Cassian Jeron Andor, also known by the aliases Willix, Aach, Joreth Sward, and the title Fulcrum, was a human male soldier, pilot and Intelligence officer who served in the Confederacy of Independent Systems during the Clone Wars and then the Alliance to Restore the Republic during Operation Fracture and the Galactic Civil War."